      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "1. Random\n\n2. Spread\n  - Default\n  - Least number of containers\n  - CPU and RAM aware\n\n3. Binpack\n  - Most num of containers\n  - CPU and RAM aware",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Random\n\n2. Spread\n  - Default\n  - Least number of containers\n  - CPU and RAM aware\n\n3. Binpack\n  - Most num of containers\n  - CPU and RAM aware",
